{"tid":155600,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【有溶屍、食屍、姦屍場面】 惠英紅拍Fox新劇：淨係知劇本吸引人","createTime":"2017-03-14T07:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T19:42:02.000Z","uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39540c8140f126bcb39526511c483f69b12b4c3a","tid":155600,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:15:02.000Z","msg":"Fox 港劇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，秋生, 惠英紅, 謝君豪 正呀 <br />\n<br />\n福斯傳媒集團（Fox Networks Group）進軍香港電視劇巿場，<span style=\"color: red;\">邀得葉念琛執導</span>，惠英紅、黃秋生、謝君豪及邵仲衡等，為華語迷你劇《心冤》演出，《心冤》為犯罪推理劇集，將於月尾開拍，飾演夫婦嘅惠英紅及黃秋生，加上謝君豪分別飾演高級督察及總督察。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56425482&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56425482%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170314&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a7cf0355\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56425482%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170314&h=03055f2d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56425482&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170314</a>"},{"pid":"5e2b737ebe6b0699e8f1c3a656054fc8d28642a8","tid":155600,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:21:22.000Z","msg":"琛哥拍電影成品似電視劇<br />\n拍電視劇會點"},{"pid":"a9dd559ce8a290364abf30a2d863139ae88605a3","tid":155600,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:30:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>琛哥拍電影成品似電視劇<br />\n拍電視劇會點</blockquote><br />\n似youtube片"},{"pid":"56bd46c691d0bfbedac14dd79c2ace97ce993183","tid":155600,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:30:48.000Z","msg":"惠英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgm